{"tid":2055061,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"[選項故] 早知當初 ( 2 )","createTime":"2020-06-07T15:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-28T00:30:59.000Z","uid":161174,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"919b1377c67fc4667c8a6bf7d9bd51ad4d08103f","tid":2055061,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T15:56:52.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，post  ( 1 )太耐冇更新，我發現推唔返上嚟<br />\n<br />\npost ( 1 )<br />\n[選項故] 早知當初<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1886216\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1886216</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為咗方便讀者追文<br />\n我嘅故會放上去<br />\n<br />\n紙言：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.shikoto.com/authors/43037.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shikoto.com%2Fauthors%2F43037.html&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3KbP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=ac483693\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.shikoto.com/authors/43037.html</a><br />\n<br />\nPenana：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/61630\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F61630&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3KbP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=1a906891\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/61630</a><br />\n<br />\n有興趣可以like作者Facebook：<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/薯皮-101753414829088/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F%E8%96%AF%E7%9A%AE-101753414829088%2F&d=jILigwfPQQ17AL812Qo3KbP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=6c44a32d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/薯皮-101753414829088/</a><br />\n我會貪得意，分享啲自己寫嘅食評<br />\n同自己做嘅手作公仔<br />\n雖然呢啲連登都有得睇<br />\n<br />\n多謝咁多位一直對我嘅支持<br />\n希望我嘅故可以帶到快樂俾大家<br />\n<br />\nkeep住鍾意睇<br />\n嚟啦<br />\n大大力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我出文啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作者其他故：<br />\n《野味小精靈》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1893783\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1893783</a>"},{"pid":"eaa95671018269a709273d82efdfb48961930273","tid":2055061,"uid":261118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T15:57:18.000Z","msg":"薯皮巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d5aadc2f51adbd8aab9ed045f9d57a00354baec","tid":2055061,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T15:58:30.000Z","msg":"而家係2015年<br />\n<br />\nA. 屌返佢老母<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n「我屌返你老母！」其實我冇話太嬲，但下意識回敬返佢一句老母，好公平啊。<br />\n<br />\n阿叔聽到之後嬲到臉都紅曬，情緒好激動，大大聲咁對我講：「nmsl.」<br />\n<br />\n四圍嘅路人聽到之後，都開始圍觀我哋。民賤聯議員喺附近開住車轉圈，嘆住冷氣，監察住我哋做野。佢見到前邊突然圍咗咁多人，都落車了解情況。<br />\n<br />\n「發生咩事啊？」民賤聯議員見有人嘈咬，於是準備出嚟解圍拎光環。<br />\n<br />\n阿叔已經俾我激到語無倫次，只係識不斷重複講「nmsl 」，我邊度嚟咁多個媽可以死了啊？<br />\n<br />\n佢一見到民賤聯議員就係我派俾佢張傳單上邊條柒頭，即刻喺佢臉前撕爛手上嘅傳單，掉向佢，然後大叫一聲：「nmsl ！」<br />\n<br />\n民賤聯議員被佢嚇到有啲呆滯，轉頭問我：「到底發生咩事啊？」<br />\n<br />\n我決定：<br />\nA. 扮忠心 (打我老細！再同阿叔舌戰3百回合)<br />\nB. 扮聽唔到，轉去其他地方派傳單<br />\nC. 老屈阿叔非禮<br />\nD. 如實話佢聽<br />\nE. 其他"},{"pid":"921a09756ec90803bdd30e9444b76c8cc548be73","tid":2055061,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eaa95671018269a709273d82efdfb48961930273","tid":2055061,"uid":261118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T15:57:18.000Z","msg":"薯皮巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T15:58:41.000Z","msg":"hi"},{"pid":"a9669bf45e186e14f34930afe66740dfab2dc309","tid":2055061,"uid":314767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T16:02:43.000Z","msg":"A"},{"pid":"5f00ad8fda0fd54b2dafe4a2a5a77684ceb2a9c2","tid":2055061,"uid":261118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"921a09756ec90803bdd30e9444b76c8cc548be73","tid":2055061,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eaa95671018269a709273d82efdfb48961930273","tid":2055061,"uid":261118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T15:57:18.000Z","msg":"薯皮巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T15:58:41.000Z","msg":"hi"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T16:17:24.000Z","msg":"Hi"},{"pid":"2b0981b23a9f51d7395b4b4b10be4300b41eeac7","tid":2055061,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f00ad8fda0fd54b2dafe4a2a5a77684ceb2a9c2","tid":2055061,"uid":261118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"921a09756ec90803bdd30e9444b76c8cc548be73","tid":2055061,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eaa95671018269a709273d82efdfb48961930273","tid":2055061,"uid":261118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T15:57:18.000Z","msg":"薯皮巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T15:58:41.000Z","msg":"hi"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T16:17:24.000Z","msg":"Hi"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T16:17:59.000Z","msg":"一齊玩啊"},{"pid":"e9794bf90ce1841d2fc33390a667230e954fdd97","tid":2055061,"uid":261118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b0981b23a9f51d7395b4b4b10be4300b41eeac7","tid":2055061,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f00ad8fda0fd54b2dafe4a2a5a77684ceb2a9c2","tid":2055061,"uid":261118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"921a09756ec90803bdd30e9444b76c8cc548be73","tid":2055061,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T15:58:41.000Z","msg":"hi"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T16:17:24.000Z","msg":"Hi"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T16:17:59.000Z","msg":"一齊玩啊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T16:19:03.000Z","msg":"玩乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da961c3b8c222c761aaa91a20f0c01867b513e58","tid":2055061,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9794bf90ce1841d2fc33390a667230e954fdd97","tid":2055061,"uid":261118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b0981b23a9f51d7395b4b4b10be4300b41eeac7","tid":2055061,"uid":161174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f00ad8fda0fd54b2dafe4a2